{"tid":972332,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"現代奴隸： 數碼奴隸 / 網路奴隸","createTime":"2019-01-07T10:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T10:40:29.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76d0097cab48e6b8183c5c5c8b8198eabf25312b","tid":972332,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:13:09.000Z","msg":"現代版奴隸：數碼奴隸 / 網路奴隸<br />\n<br />\n結合網路及人類成癮心理及心理強迫效果<br />\n制造出令你上癮的網路<br />\n自動獻身<br />\n讓你無私奉獻給網路世界<br />\n<br />\nWikipedia 就係號召世界上所有網路奴隸，自願無私地奉獻工作，最成功的典範。<br />\n<br />\nTypical Modern digital slave life <br />\n典型的網路奴隸生活<br />\n<br />\nA: Hey friends, let us take a rest<br />\nB: No. There is something wrong on the interne t and I try to fix it. <br />\n<br />\nA: Hello, boys and girls, Let's take a rest.<br />\nC: No. Some people posting stupid idea and wrong information, I wanna correct them.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/07/180957_f0ce6c7641ebcdb2d8094b21f2a18fe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F07%2F180957_f0ce6c7641ebcdb2d8094b21f2a18fe6.png&h=b98bb698&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2420367dc2b487f8c7b52774e1e1265abd094e49","tid":972332,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"How we're becoming slaves to technology, explained by an MIT sociologist <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vox.com/science-and-health/2018/3/27/17085282/technology-facebook-social-media-sherry-turkle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fscience-and-health%2F2018%2F3%2F27%2F17085282%2Ftechnology-facebook-social-media-sherry-turkle&d=6F2wiYdL7XsyXFQWHa%2BeTTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b37ecc20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.vox.com/science-and-health/2018/3/27/17085282/technology-facebook-social-media-sherry-turkle</a>"},{"pid":"285d439e9c9a90c603b2a78986ab2c0dbc333e5d","tid":972332,"uid":510